name: TurboTax 2021 Tax Return
summary: A TAX2021 file contains a United States tax return created with the 2021 version of Intuit TurboTax. It stores tax return information for the 2021 tax year, which typically includes personal data entered by a user, a federal IRS tax form, and one or more state forms. TAX2021 files may be created by the 2021 desktop version or exported and downloaded by the 2021 online version of TurboTax.
